query: SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS character_name, MIN(mi_idx.info) AS rating, MIN(n.name) AS playing_actor, MIN(t.title) AS complete_hero_movie FROM complete_cast AS cc, comp_cast_type AS cct1, comp_cast_type AS cct2, char_name AS chn, cast_info AS ci, info_type AS it2, keyword AS k, kind_type AS kt, movie_info_idx AS mi_idx, movie_keyword AS mk, name AS n, title AS t WHERE kt.id = t.kind_id AND t.id = mk.movie_id AND t.id = ci.movie_id AND t.id = cc.movie_id AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = ci.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND cc.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id AND n.id = ci.person_id AND k.id = mk.keyword_id AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id AND cct2.id = cc.status_id AND it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id AND n.gender not in ('f') AND kt.kind in ('video game','episode','tv mini series','tv movie','movie','video movie') AND (k.keyword like '%terror%' OR k.keyword like '%power%') AND cct2.kind not in ('complete','cast') AND mi_idx.info < '2.0' AND it2.info not in ('LD original title','LD contrast','LD audio quality','salary history','LD video quality','LD disc format','rentals','countries','LD supplement','keywords','LD frequency response','LD color information','LD label','LD quality program','runtimes','LD catalog number','LD release country','other literature','LD language','tech info') AND chn.name not like '%Iron Man%' AND (t.title like '%doll%' OR t.title like '%thriller%') AND cct1.kind in ('crew','complete')
